Name: Erdling

text:
Erdling (German for "Earthling") are a German Neue Deutsche Härte band founded in 2014 from former band members of the band Stahlmann.
The band members include Neill Freiwald (vocals, guitar, programming), Neno Knuckle (guitar), Christian Eichlinger (drums), and Robin Sem Vedrfölnir (bass guitar).[1]

Singer Neill Freiwald
Guitarist Neno Knuckle
Drummer Christian Eichlinger
Bass Guitarist Pierre Anders
